Package: koon
Title: Browser-Impersonating HTTP Client
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: person("scrape-hub", email = "scrape-hub@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: HTTP client that impersonates real browser TLS, HTTP/2 and HTTP/3
    fingerprints. Supports Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge, and Opera profiles.
    Passes Akamai, Cloudflare, and other bot detection systems by reproducing
    exact browser fingerprints verified against real browser captures.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc >= 1.85
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: jsonlite, knitr, rmarkdown, testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/rextendr/version: 0.4.2
